ZH: 我看到一只小狗躺在角落里。
EN: I saw a little dog lying in the corner.
ZH: 那个女孩一直躲在角落里。
EN: The girl kept hiding in the corner.
ZH: 我喜欢坐在教室的角落读书。
EN: I like sitting in the corner of the classroom to read.
ZH: 她把书放在书架的角落里。
EN: She placed the books in the corner of the bookshelf.
ZH: 我看到一条小跳蚤在床角落里。
EN: I saw a small flea in the corner of the bed.
ZH: 请把椅子放到房间的某个角落里。
EN: Please place the chair in some corner of the room.
ZH: 这家咖啡馆的最佳座位在一楼的窗户角落里。
EN: The best seats at this cafe are in the corner by the window on the first floor.
ZH: 爷爷安静地坐在沙发角落。
EN: Grandpa sat quietly in the corner of the sofa.
ZH: 我发现你把钱藏在了抽屉的角落。
EN: I found you hiding the money in the corner of the drawer.
ZH: 孩子们喜欢在房间里闪烁的灯光角落玩耍。
EN: The children like playing in the corners of the room where the lights flicker.
ZH: 这个城市的许多故事都隐藏在角落里。
EN: Many stories of this city hide in its corners.
ZH: 角落里有一个蜘蛛网。
EN: There is a spider web in the corner.
ZH: 她被锁在一个黑暗的角落里。
EN: She was locked in a dark corner.
ZH: 我常常把我的心事深藏在心底的角落。
EN: I often keep my troubles hidden in the corner of my heart.
ZH: 他站在街角落，观察着人来人往。
EN: He stood at the street corner, observing the passersby.
ZH: 小偷躲在街角的阴影里。
EN: The thief hid in the shadow of the street corner.
ZH: 这个城市的美景到处都是，不仅仅在触角落。
EN: The beauty of this city is everywhere, not just in the corners.
ZH: 角落里有一份你的生日礼物。
EN: There is a birthday present for you in the corner.
ZH: 小猫一直躲在角落里，害怕出来。
EN: The kitten kept hiding in the corner, afraid to come out.
ZH: 数不清的回忆都埋葬在角落里了。
EN: Countless memories are buried in the corners.
